{"tid":1465000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家對準方向 要記住無論如何 不割","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:49:02.000Z","uid":232968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"537669fd2693f4bd8ed330fb0bf4d30ce26a2ee9","tid":1465000,"uid":232968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"相信大家透過各大傳媒，係現場嘅朋友，見到8月13號機場嘅捉到公安事件<br />\n我相信好多人呢一刻好多諗法，諗緊係咪好多鬼，點解前線會失晒控咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我 只 可 以 講 前 線 有 情 緒</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無論呢一刻前線做左d乜事 係比人煽動又好 壓抑左好耐以黎嘅壓力都好<br />\n千祈唔好怪責前線 可能你唔認同佢呢一刻嘅做法 覺得佢地失晒理智<br />\n但係 記住 大家都係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同路人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家可以憤怒 大家可以好嬲 但係請記住 政府同埋警權係呢兩個月對我地所做嘅一切<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遠超</span></span></strong>今日機場手足所做嘅事<br />\n<br />\n與其站係道德高地怪責手足 不如對準方向<br />\n諗下點對向我地嘅敵人作出更有效嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈譴責</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不割蓆不譴責不篤灰</strong></span>"},{"pid":"13f5ed4101fdce03eb6d6cd4cef06f5a6024f75a","tid":1465000,"uid":232968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"261e5c772cec2c2d2b882c91f4e56de7f977e8da","tid":1465000,"uid":232968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"790ec10d309345d768d91b79fefb97446baff7fd","tid":1465000,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"香港咁多中共國企 點解反而去搞自己啲公共設施<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDzhmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDzhmS</a>"},{"pid":"eb275fc28fbb0058489b62c89fef3680881a6166","tid":1465000,"uid":232968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}